<template><div><h1 id="camel-case" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#camel-case" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Camel Case</h1>
<p><a href="https://npmjs.org/package/camel-case" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/camel-case.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>
<a href="https://npmjs.org/package/camel-case" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/camel-case.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>
<a href="https://bundlephobia.com/result?p=camel-case" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/bundlephobia/minzip/camel-case.svg" alt="Bundle size"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Transform into a string with the separator denoted by the next word capitalized.</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="installation" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#installation" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Installation</h2>
<div class="language-text ext-text line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>npm install camel-case --save
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> camelCase <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> <span class="token string">"camel-case"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token function">camelCase</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"string"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">//=> "string"</span>
<span class="token function">camelCase</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"dot.case"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">//=> "dotCase"</span>
<span class="token function">camelCase</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"PascalCase"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">//=> "pascalCase"</span>
<span class="token function">camelCase</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"version 1.2.10"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">//=> "version_1_2_10"</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>The function also accepts <a href="https://github.com/blakeembrey/change-case#options" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code v-pre>options</code><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>.</p>
<h3 id="merge-numbers" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#merge-numbers" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Merge Numbers</h3>
<p>If you'd like to remove the behavior prefixing <code v-pre>_</code> before numbers, you can use <code v-pre>camelCaseTransformMerge</code>:</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> camelCaseTransformMerge <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> <span class="token string">"camel-case"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token function">camelCase</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"version 12"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token literal-property property">transform</span><span class="token operator">:</span> camelCaseTransformMerge <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment">//=> "version12"</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="license" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#license" aria-hidden="true">#</a> License</h2>
<p>MIT</p>
</div></template>
